import React, { Component } from "react";
import {
  Button,
  Form,
  FormGroup,
  Label,
  Input,
  Container,
  Col,
} from "reactstrap";

export default class LoginComponent extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
      <Container>
        <Col md={6}>
          <Form>
            <FormGroup>
              <Label for="Username">Username</Label>
              <Input
                required
                type="text"
                name="text"
                id="textUser"
                placeholder="Masukkan Username..."
              />
            </FormGroup>
            <FormGroup>
              <Label for="Password">Password</Label>
              <Input
                required
                type="password"
                name="password"
                id="textPassword"
                placeholder="Masukkan Password..."
              />
            </FormGroup>
            <Button>Submit</Button>
          </Form>
        </Col>
      </Container>
    );
  }
}
